allowance(address,address).details: Returns allowance of token to spender

approve(address,uint256).details: Owner call this function allow spender to transfer their token

params._spender: Address that can transfer owner's token

burn(address,uint256).details: Only owner of the token can burn thier token

params.amount: Number of tokens to be burn

decreaseAllowance(address,uint256).details: Owner decrease allowance of spender to spend less tokens

params.spender: Address that can transfer owner's token

getOwner().details: Return current owner of the contract

increaseAllowance(address,uint256).details: Owner increase allowance of spender to spend more tokens

params.spender: Address that can transfer owner's token

params.amount: Number of tokens to be mint

transfer(address,uint256).details: Owner transfer token from their address to receiver

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: Spender transfer token which owner allowed them

transferOwnership(address).details: owner of the contract transfer onwership to new owner
